{"id":154723,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/科学家用干细胞培育出人脑星状细胞/","date":"2011-05-23T20:30:52Z","modified":"2011-05-23T20:30:52Z","title":"科学家用干细胞培育出人脑星状细胞","content":"<p>星形胶质细胞（astrocyte）或称星状细胞，是大脑中最常见的细胞，它们为神经元提供关键支持功能，如引导神经元移动，提供神经元所需的营养，维持神经元周围的离子平衡。这种细胞也被认为与某些大脑疾病有关联。根据《自然生物技术》期刊上发表的研究，威斯康星大学的研究人员找到了方法，用干细胞培育出星状细胞。领导这项研究的Su-Chun Zhang教授指出，理解星状细胞功能，将能帮助研究人员为神经性失调症状发明新疗法与新药物。“这些细胞还没有得到许多关注，因为人类星状细胞很难获得。但我们能从单一干细胞制造出十亿或上兆个星状细胞。”<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/151809f1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%91%E6%98%9F%E7%8A%B6%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F23%2F0633201%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%91%E6%98%9F%E7%8A%B6%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F23%2F0633201%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093618737/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/151809f1/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093618737/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/151809f1/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cvgbmPWbnc0:-zrwDsDQzZs:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cvgbmPWbnc0:-zrwDsDQzZs:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0